P SLNA VS HAGL</span></u></span><u><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><br>\r\n</span></u></strong><br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4455","checkdouble":"191726"},{"date":"14:34 21/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 18h00 ng\u00e0y 21/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/thanh-hoa-vs-ha-noi-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u FLC Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 18h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 21/7.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u FLC Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 18h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 21/7.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/thanh-hoa-vs-ha-noi-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191730.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP THANH H\u00d3A VS H\u00c0 N\u1ed8I</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4454","checkdouble":"191730"},{"date":"17:55 21/07","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 SLNA vs HAGL tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/26/ket-qua-slna-vs-hagl-tran-dau-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 SLNA vs HAGL tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, video b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, clip highlights tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u SLNA S\u00f4ng Lam Ngh\u1ec7 An vs HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 21/7.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p 1: SLNA 2-0 HAGL<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: Olaha (13'), Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh (45'+2).</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 20 V-League, c\u1ea3 SLNA vs HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SLNA l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 hai, Olaha x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u00e1 hay b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i r\u1ed3i t\u1ea1t v\u00e0o trong cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i h\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"SLNA vs HAGL\" title=\"SLNA vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/6_Zing_3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>SLNA thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n HAGL trong hi\u1ec7p 1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 SLNA ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i \u0111i thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, HAGL v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, v\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Olaha \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 13 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdc khe thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olaha v\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i binh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm gi\u00fap tr\u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n, tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi d\u00f9 Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc hay C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nguy hi\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7p 1 s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a SLNA th\u00ec \u0111\u00fang \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 2, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap SLNA v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng sau 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#222222;mso-fareast-language:KO\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4453","checkdouble":"191739"},{"date":"12:27 21/07","title":"\"Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u0169 kh\u00f4ng n\u00e3o m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Neymar\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/12/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ea5u m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil t\u1ea1o ra t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t leo thang, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dani Alves l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn \u00e1c \u00fd.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nAlves l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e3o ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 Neymar<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u1ee7a Neymar kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Brazil ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, th\u00f3i quen \u0103n v\u1ea1 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Neymar tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh r\u1ea5t x\u1ea5u x\u00ed tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u th\u00f3i \u201cdi\u1ec5n s\u00e2u\u201d c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng clip \u0103n v\u1ea1 l\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0103n v\u1ea1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i qu\u00e1 xa, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dani Alves \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Alves cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cKh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00f9a. Khi n\u00f3 l\u1eb7p \u0111i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i, s\u1ef1 vui v\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 cho nh\u1eefng t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e2u s\u1eafc.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 nh\u1eefng con ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00f4ng minh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 nh\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Neymar s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o ch\u00ednh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 b\u1ea1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dani Alves l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Neymar v\u00ec th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Dani Alves l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Neymar v\u00ec th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Dani-Alves-len-tieng-bao-ve-Neymar-vi-thoi-an-va-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Dani Alves l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Neymar</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Dani Alves c\u0169ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real Madrid c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i: \u201cTh\u00fa th\u1ef1c, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Neymar \u0111ang r\u1ea5t m\u01a1 h\u1ed3. Nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i PSG c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i n\u0103m n\u00e0y qua n\u0103m kh\u00e1c. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cNh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Khi \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u, nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i PSG, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ra \u0111i ch\u1eebng n\u00e0o ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh n\u00f3\u201d \u2013 Dani Alves l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Neymar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/neymar-tin-ronaldo-se-toa-sang-tren-dat-y-176-191698.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/neymar-tin-ronaldo-se-toa-sang-tren-dat-y.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/neymar-tin-ronaldo-se-toa-sang-tren-dat-y-176-191698.html\">Neymar tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u00dd</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o PSG nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 anh t\u1eebng th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c thu\u1edf nh\u1ecf, v\u1edbi gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/neymar-la-cau-thu-bong-da-thu-hai-dat-100-trieu-theo-doi-tren-instagram-188-191559.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/phong-do-va-dang-cap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/neymar-la-cau-thu-bong-da-thu-hai-dat-100-trieu-theo-doi-tren-instagram-188-191559.html\">Neymar l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u1ea1t 100 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i tr\u00ean Instagram</span><br>\r\nT\u00ednh ri\u00eang \u1edf World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n Brazil c\u00f3 th\u00eam 10 tri\u1ec7u theo d\u00f5i tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i chuy\u00ean chia s\u1ebb \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 video.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4452","checkdouble":"191719"},{"date":"13:22 21/07","title":"Neymar ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Mbappe","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/10/6/neymar-chang-co-van-de-gi-voi-mbappe.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, nh\u01b0ng Neymar kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Mbappe \u2013 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch PSG.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nNeymar v\u00e0 Mbappe c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn PSG \u0111\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Messi, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng Neymar s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho Kylian Mbappe &ndash; t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Trong khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ea5u v\u00ec th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1, sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u1ea1i CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00e2n HLV Tuchel n\u00ean t\u1eadp trung ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n Mbappe, thay v\u00ec nu\u00f4ng chi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao \u0103n v\u1ea1 Neymar. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a PSG cho r\u1eb1ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t h\u00f2a thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi nhau&rdquo; &ndash; \u00f4ng Nasser Al-Khelaifi chia s\u1ebb. &ldquo;M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eau d\u1ec7t b\u1edfi c\u00e1nh nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn gi\u1eefa b\u1ecdn h\u1ecd, c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 vui v\u1ebb khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nhau.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Mbappe\" title=\"Coutinho s\u1edbm s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 ba th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi sau Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/7/Nhung-con-so-biet-noi-xung-quanh-qua-sieu-bom-tan-Coutinho-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Mbappe</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng: ch\u1eb3ng ai trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ra \u0111i. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p. \u0110T Brazil \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, trong khi Ph\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Kylian Mbappe th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c, c\u00f2n Neymar c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t&rdquo; &ndash; Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch PSG cho bi\u1ebft.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Mbappe, v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea3 2 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, d\u00f9 Real Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang khao kh\u00e1t c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-toi-dang-co-ru-re-mbappe-toi-liverpool-172-191637.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/fabinho-toi-dang-co-ru-re-mbappe-toi-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-toi-dang-co-ru-re-mbappe-toi-liverpool-172-191637.html\">Fabinho: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 r\u1ee7 r\u00ea Mbappe t\u1edbi Liverpool&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Monaco, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fabinho thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Mbappe t\u1edbi Liverpool &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kylian-mbappe-mon-qua-duoc-ban-tang-cho-bong-da-421-191618.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/kylian-mbappe-mon-qua-duoc-ban-tang-cho-bong-da.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kylian-mbappe-mon-qua-duoc-ban-tang-cho-bong-da-421-191618.html\">Kylian Mbappe: M\u00f3n qu\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ban t\u1eb7ng cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><br>\r\nC\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac th\u00f4i, k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t k\u1ebb th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c, ai \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Th\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0110\u1ebf ban t\u1eb7ng cho...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kylian-mbappe-thien-tai-va-ke-phan-dien-trong-hinh-hai-chang-trai-19-421-190918.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/hazd-thu-linh-cua-quy-do.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kylian-mbappe-thien-tai-va-ke-phan-dien-trong-hinh-hai-chang-trai-19-421-190918.html\">Kylian Mbappe: Thi\u00ean t\u00e0i v\u00e0 k\u1ebb ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n trong h\u00ecnh h\u00e0i ch\u00e0ng trai 19</span><br>\r\nCh\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta m\u1edbi th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 2 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Kylian Mbappe trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4451","checkdouble":"191720"},{"date":"13:12 21/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern Munich vs PSG 21h05 ng\u00e0y 21/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/nhan-dinh-bayern-munich-vs-psg-21h05-ngay-217-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bayern Munich vs PSG l\u00fac 21h05 ng\u00e0y 21/7 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern Munich vs PSG 21h05 ng\u00e0y 217 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern Munich vs PSG 21h05 ng\u00e0y 217 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2172018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bayern Munich vs PSG</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Bayern Munich vs PSG: 3-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u00ec v\u1ecdng, c\u1ea3 Bayern Munich v\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u1ec1u \u201cthay m\u00e1u\u201d b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. H\u00f9m x\u00e1m b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Niko Kovac thay cho chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia l\u00e3o l\u00e0ng Jupp Heynckes quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Parc des Princes l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Thomas Tuchel, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ch\u00ednh Bayern \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i t\u00ecm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i thay cho Unai Emery.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m chung c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y l\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh ti\u1ebfng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng khi m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 1 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0 C\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c. V\u00e0 tr\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, vinh quang \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi h\u1ecd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi CLB c\u0169. L\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i g\u1eb7p nhau, Tuchel c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh Kovac \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m chung th\u00fa v\u1ecb tr\u00ean, c\u1ea3 Kovac v\u00e0 Tuchel \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00ec v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd th\u1ed5i lu\u1ed3ng gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Bayern l\u1eabn PSG. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 chung ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n khi mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u00edch c\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi th\u1ee9 v\u0169 kh\u00ed ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu n\u00ean kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0o hay h\u01a1n. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean mang \u0111\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00c1o \u0111\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng h\u1ea3o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf World Cup. Ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, Bayern \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n khi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 khung v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 David Alaba, Arturo Vidal, Javi Martinez v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1nh Arjen Robben \u2013 Franck Ribery. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Renato Sanches, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o qu\u00ean l\u00e3ng nh\u01b0ng qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u1edbi HLV Kovac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n so t\u00e0i gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean nh\u01b0 Lukas Mai, Meritan Shabani (Bayern) hay Timothy Weah, Christopher Nkunku (PSG) c\u0169ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng xem. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u201cm\u0103ng non\u201d s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai hai \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1eed l\u1eeda \u1edf v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1edfi m\u1edf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. S\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n, Bayern l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1eafm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua PSG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\nBAYERN: V\u1eafng c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao tham d\u1ef1 World Cup.<br>\r\nPSG: Ngo\u00e0i c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong k\u00ec ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup c\u00f2n v\u1eafng Dani Alves v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPHONG \u0110\u1ed8 V\u00c0 \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Bayern thua c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n- 4 tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1i Ligue 1, PSG h\u00f2a 3, thua 1.<br>\r\n-  Hai \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p nhau 8 l\u1ea7n \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, Bayern th\u1eafng 3,  PSG th\u1eafng 5. 2 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4450","checkdouble":"191723"},{"date":"17:01 21/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Bayern Munich vs PSG 21h05 ng\u00e0y 21/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/21/bayern-munich-vs-psg-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Bayern Munich vs PSG: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Bayern vs PSG gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 21h05 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 21/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPH\u00c1T BI\u1ec2U<br>\r\nHLV Niko Kovac (Bayern): \u201cPSG l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Bayern\u201d.<br>\r\nHLV Thomas Tuchel (PSG): \u201cTh\u1eadt vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p Bayern trong t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a PSG. T\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c, Bayern l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1. Nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, PSG c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ed1 1 t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00fa v\u1ecb\u201d.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Bayern Munich vs PSG t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 217 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Bayern Munich vs PSG t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 217 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/nhan-dinh-bayern-munich-vs-psg-21h05-ngay-217-icc-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bayern Munich vs PSG</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\n- Bayern to\u00e0n thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n- 9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Bayern, c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 7 tr\u1eadn c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi trong 2 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Champions League 2017/18.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1eb5n: 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Bayern, c\u00f3 3 tr\u1eadn k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1eb5n. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, 11 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a PSG c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 9 tr\u1eadn k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung l\u00e0 ch\u1eb5n. K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n tr\u00ean s\u1ebd l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4449","checkdouble":"191741"},{"date":"14:22 21/07","title":"Real Madrid chi ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/real-muon-mua-trippier-cua-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Trippier, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh. Los Blancos s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Trippier t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi gia nh\u1eadp Tottenham t\u1eeb Burnley n\u0103m 2015, Kieran Trippier \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0110T Anh tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Trippier c\u00f2n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nguy hi\u1ec3m trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u201cb\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft\u201d, g\u1ee3i nh\u1edb t\u1edbi c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 David Beckham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real mu\u1ed1n mua Trippier, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real mu\u1ed1n mua Trippier, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/real-muon-mua-trippier-cua-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Trippier ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrippier l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Croatia. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 1-2 v\u00e0 d\u00f9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real chi \u0111\u1eadm cho Trippier</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh cho hay Real Madrid \u0111ang d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m cho Trippier. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 3 n\u0103m, Tottenham ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf 3,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Trippier. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kieran Trippier\" title=\"Kieran Trippier\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/16/Doi-hinh-sieu-khung-ket-hop-giua-Tottenham-vs-Arsenal-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Trippier v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Trippier b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi anh v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Real m\u1edbi chi 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alvaro Odriozola t\u1eeb Real Sociedad v\u00e0 c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu Dani Carvajal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi Real chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Trippier khi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 l\u00e0 thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu l\u00e0 Trippier c\u00f3 chung ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Jonathan Barnett v\u1edbi Gareth Bale, ch\u1ea5t x\u00fac t\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Wales r\u1eddi Spurs gi\u00e1 86 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng n\u0103m 2013.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a-180-191701.html\">Real mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201cs\u00e1t th\u1ee7\u201d Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-quan-tam-toi-jasper-cillessen-172-191681.html\">S\u1ee3 Real 'c\u01b0\u1edbp' ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Chelsea v\u1ed9i v\u00e3 h\u1ecfi mua sao Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nham-joe-hart-thay-courtois-172-191722.html\">C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1i t\u00ean Chelsea nh\u1eafm thay Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/keylor-navas-khong-ngai-canh-tranh-vi-tri-voi-courtois-180-191679.html\">Keylor Navas kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4448","checkdouble":"191727"},{"date":"14:50 21/07","title":"\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi mua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Lucas Digne c\u1ee7a Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh dung c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y Digne</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016, Barcelona b\u1ecf s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 13.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (16.5 tri\u1ec7u Euro) \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lucas Digne t\u1eeb PSG. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou t\u1eebng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho Jordi Alba.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian 2 n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua, Digne v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Alba. \u0110\u00e3 th\u1ebf, \u1edf nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n hi\u1ebfm hoi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u. C\u1ea3 tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hay ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c HLV Barca h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Lucas Digne gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Lucas Digne gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Digne g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0<br>\r\nTruy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a tin Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Digne ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Everton \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd mua Digne</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb t\u1edd Mirror, Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Lucas Digne. H\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 6 tri\u1ec7u so v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Lucas Digne gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Lucas Digne gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/lucas-digne-chuan-bi-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Lucas Digne gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a Everton, Marco Silva tin r\u1eb1ng Digne c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebf nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Leighton Baines. 11 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, Baines lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a The Toffees b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang tr\u00e1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n 34 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Everton, nh\u1eefng Juventus v\u00e0 Bayern Munich c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m cho Digne. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1eadt b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ra gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-bao-tin-cuc-vui-cho-mu-va-barca-172-191646.html\">Sao kh\u1ee7ng Chelsea b\u00e1o tin c\u1ef1c vui cho MU v\u00e0 Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ajax-gui-canh-bao-danh-thep-toi-barca-180-191626.html\">Nh\u0103m nhe sao tr\u1ebb, Barca nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o g\u1eaft t\u1eeb Ajax</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-barca-cap-ben-nou-camp-nho-neymar-180-191543.html\">T\u00e2n binh Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Nou Camp nh\u1edd Neymar</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-quyet-dau-voi-real-vi-eden-hazard-180-191467.html\">Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real v\u00ec Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/andre-gomes-muon-toi-tottenham-172-191411.html\">Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f9ng Harry Kane t\u1ea1i Premier League</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4447","checkdouble":"191729"},{"date":"17:41 21/07","title":"Xavi ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i thay Iniesta cho Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/21/xavi-tien-cu-rabiot-cho-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Xavi ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed Rabiot cho Barca. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia m\u1edbi chia tay b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paulinho, Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Xavi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Barca mua Rabiot</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho hay Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou s\u1ebd chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kho\u1ea3ng 40 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 Paulinho ra \u0111i l\u1ea1i c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1eefng Andre Gomes hay Denis Suarez g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1. Xavi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Blaugrana tin r\u1eb1ng Rabiot s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xavi ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed Rabiot cho Barca trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Iniesta h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xavi ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed Rabiot cho Barca trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Iniesta h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/xavi-tien-cu-rabiot-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt\u201d, Xavi ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed Rabiot cho Barca tr\u00ean t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o t\u1ea1i Barca. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u1ebfu gia nh\u1eadp.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 Griezmann r\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico. N\u1ebfu h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Rabiot ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho Barca.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i Arthur</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 Arthur Melo t\u1eeb Gremio v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 39 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Xavi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 DNA c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia song tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho anh n\u1ebfu b\u1ecb so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh hay Iniesta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xavi cua Barca\" title=\"Xavi cua Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Xavi-cua-Barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Xavi ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed Rabiot cho Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 xem m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i video v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Arthur. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil t\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n Aspire (Qatar) \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Al Sadd n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho Barca. Arthur c\u00f3 c\u00e1i m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 DNA Barca.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t. C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f9ng xem Arthur c\u00f3 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn hay ch\u01b0a. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Barca l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang-172-191729.html\">\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi mua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea-187-191704.html\">G\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n 3, Barca quy\u1ebft mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lucas-digne-chuan-bi-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191654.html\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-bao-tin-cuc-vui-cho-mu-va-barca-172-191646.html\">Sao kh\u1ee7ng Chelsea b\u00e1o tin c\u1ef1c vui cho MU v\u00e0 Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ajax-gui-canh-bao-danh-thep-toi-barca-180-191626.html\">Nh\u0103m nhe sao tr\u1ebb, Barca nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o g\u1eaft t\u1eeb Ajax</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4446","checkdouble":"191740"},{"date":"15:59 21/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Liverpool s\u1eafp chia tay Danny Ings","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/21/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-liverpool-sap-chia-tay-danny-ings.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Danny Ings r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng The Kop tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 di chuy\u1ec3n sang M\u1ef9 tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018, The Kop s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Klopp th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u00f4ng tham gia du \u0111\u1ea5u, Danny Ings r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u00f4ng tham gia du \u0111\u1ea5u, Danny Ings r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/21/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-liverpool-sap-chia-tay-danny-ings.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danny Ings kh\u00f4ng tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Dortmund v\u00e0o 3h05 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam).</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDanh s\u00e1ch 29 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba Mohamed Salah, Sadio Mane v\u00e0 Marko Grujic \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. 4 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng b\u1ed9 ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi ng\u1edd r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Danny Ings. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Danny Ings s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Danny Ings r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u00f4ng tham gia du \u0111\u1ea5u, Danny Ings r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u00f4ng tham gia du \u0111\u1ea5u, Danny Ings r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/20/danny-ings-thua-nhan-hoc-theo-firmino-de-lay-lai-phong-do-tot-nhat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danny Ings s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDanny Ings chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Liverpool t\u1eeb Burnley c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 3 n\u0103m, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Brendan Rodgers \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao, song ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u cho Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Klopp, Ings c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i r\u1ea5t ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 25 l\u1ea7n k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Burnley t\u1edbi Liverpool, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c The Kop \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ings \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Anfield. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Crystal Palace, Celtic, Southampton v\u00e0 Bournemouth.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/southampton-chi-20-trieu-bang-mua-tien-dao-cua-liverpool-172-191262.html\" target=\"_blank\">Southampton mua Danny Ings</span> th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 cao nh\u1ea5t, Daily Echo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4445","checkdouble":"191735"},{"date":"16:48 21/07","title":"T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/jeremie-boga-roi-chelsea-toi-sassuolo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jeremie Boga r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Sassuolo. Sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho 3 CLB kh\u00e1c nhau m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong th\u1eddi gian qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB Serie A mua \u0111\u1ee9t.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Boga li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJeremie Boga sinh ng\u00e0y 3 th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 1997 t\u1ea1i Marseille trong m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh g\u1ed1c B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0. Anh gia nh\u1eadp l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t CLB nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c trinh s\u00e1t vi\u00ean Chelsea ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 n\u0103m 2009. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay, Boga ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Chelsea. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a The Blues t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, song c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 18 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Christensen v\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 Gary Cahill nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jeremie Boga r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Sassuolo gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jeremie Boga r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Sassuolo gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/jeremie-boga-roi-chelsea-toi-sassuolo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Jeremie Boga r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Sassuolo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3, Boga li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t t\u1edbi Rennes (Ph\u00e1p), Granada (T\u00e2y Ban Nha) r\u1ed3i Birmingham (Anh).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Sassuolo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u00f9a 2017/18, Boga nh\u1eafn l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecb cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 21, anh tin m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 CLB, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 Boga r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Sassuolo. Anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp CLB c\u1ee7a Serie A theo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. Theo gi\u1edbi th\u1ea1o tin, m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed Sassuolo b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Boga r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 3.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2017/18, Sassuolo x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 11 tr\u00ean BXH Serie A. Boga l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 8 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd sau nh\u1eefng Federico Di Francesco, Khouma Babacar, Jens Odgaard, Mehdi Bourabia, Leonardo Sernicola, Filip Djuricic v\u00e0 Kevin-Prince Boateng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-se-ban-kante-cho-psg-neu-172-191721.html\">Chelsea s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Kante cho PSG n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea-187-191704.html\">G\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n 3, Barca quy\u1ebft mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-tu-choi-phu-phang-de-nghi-chuyen-nhuong-cua-chelsea-172-191702.html\">Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-quan-tam-toi-jasper-cillessen-172-191681.html\">S\u1ee3 Real 'c\u01b0\u1edbp' ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Chelsea v\u1ed9i v\u00e3 h\u1ecfi mua sao Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4444","checkdouble":"191736"},{"date":"16:22 21/07","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 21/07","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-2107.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 21/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Toby Alderweireld</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2107 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2107 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-viec-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-alderweireld.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U kh\u00f4ng mua Alderweireld \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham. V\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Alderweireld v\u1edbi Spurs ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, khi \u0111\u00f3 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-viec-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-alderweireld-172-191725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-viec-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-alderweireld.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-viec-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-alderweireld-172-191725.html\">Mourinho n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c MU chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alderweireld?</span><br>\r\nJose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Toby Alderweireld, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua ng\u00f4i sao...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Matteo Darmian c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi M.U v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Metteo Darmian \u0111ang c\u00f9ng M.U tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, song ESPN kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Old Trafford. Hi\u1ec7n Roma, Inter Milan v\u00e0 Juventus l\u00e0 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ef1u sao Torino.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng cho Gareth Bale</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale se quyet tam chung to minh khi Ronaldo ra di\" title=\"Bale s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh khi Ronaldo ra \u0111i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/HLV-Lopetegui-quyet-khong-de-Gareth-Bale-roi-Real-Madrid--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n Bale h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 400.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, M.U kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 400.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Gareth Bale. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho mu\u1ed1n 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1eefa \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Bill Rice c\u1ee7a BBC HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb BL\u0110 M.U mua th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eefa trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Eric Bailly</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Express kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 Eric Bailly, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Old&nbsp;Trafford v\u00ec m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng hot World Cup 2018 kh\u00f4ng gia nh\u1eadp M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hirving Lozano gieo rac con ac mong cho DT Duc.\" title=\"Hirving Lozano gieo r\u1eafc c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng cho \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/DT-Duc-thua-soc-truoc-Mexico-Low-da-thuc-su-het-bai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hirving Lozano s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Old Trafford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o H\u00e0 Lan Eindhovens Dagblad, ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Hirving Lozano ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Old Trafford \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Theo \u0111\u00f3 PSV Eindhoven \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU kh\u00f4ng mua Robert Lewandowski</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua Robert Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alex Sandro&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alex Sandro c\u1ee7a Juventus l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a PSG, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t M.U v\u1ee5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4443","checkdouble":"191737"}]}